acAVazquez\"],\"jobTitle\":\"Technical Product Manager & UC Berkeley MBA Candidate\"},\"articleSection\":\"Fantasy Football\",\"wordCount\":3449,\"keywords\":\"fantasy football beginners, how to play fantasy football, fantasy football guide 2025, fantasy football for dummies, fantasy football basics, fantasy football tutorial\"}8:[[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"@id\\\":\\\"https://isaacavazquez.com#breadcrumb\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Home\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://isaacavazquez.com/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Writing\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Fantasy Football for Beginners: Your Complete 2025 Starter Guide\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/fantasy-football-beginners-complete-guide\\\"}]}\"},\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true}],[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$11\"},\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"min-h-screen py-16 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"article\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"header\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-4\",\"children\":\"Fantasy Football for Beginners: Your Complete 2025 Starter Guide\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-4 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"time\",null,{\"dateTime\":\"2025-01-24\",\"children\":\"January 23, 2025\"}],[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"•\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"1